<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[YeonhwaBlog]]></title><description><![CDATA[하나하나 차근차근 쌓아가는 블로그]]></description><link>https://yeonhwakim.github.io</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Dec 2020 12:40:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[EP.1 블로그를 만들기 까지...]]></title><description><![CDATA[오늘 드디어 블로그를 만들게 되었다.
생각보다 많은 우여곡절이 있어서 첫번째 포스팅에 적어보려고한다.🚗🚓🚕 💦 템플릿 고르기 
💦 배포방법 
💦 permission denied? 
💦 github action…]]></description><link>https://yeonhwakim.github.io/TIL/블로그를-만들기-까지.../</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://yeonhwakim.github.io/TIL/블로그를-만들기-까지.../</guid><pubDate>Thu, 05 Nov 2020 23:12:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;오늘 드디어 블로그를 만들게 되었다.&lt;br&gt;
생각보다 많은 우여곡절이 있어서 첫번째 포스팅에 적어보려고한다.🚗🚓🚕&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#template&quot;&gt;템플릿 고르기&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#deploy&quot;&gt;배포방법&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#denied&quot;&gt;permission denied?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
💦 &lt;a href=&quot;#gitaction&quot;&gt;github action&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;template&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-템플릿-고르기-jekyll-vs-gatsby&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A5%B4%EA%B8%B0-jekyll-vs-gatsby&quot; aria-label=&quot; 템플릿 고르기 jekyll vs gatsby permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 템플릿 고르기 Jekyll vs Gatsby&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;선택 장애가 있어 템플릿을 고를 때부터 머리가 아팠다.
거두절미하고 Jekyll &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;minimal-mistakes&lt;/code&gt; 와 Gatsby &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/code&gt;가 최종 선택지였다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;결국 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/code&gt;를 선택하게 되었다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SPA고 pc는 물론 mobile 반응형 화면까지 깔끔하다.
그리고 배포도 간단해보였다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;deploy&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-배포방법-publish-with-netlify-vs-github-pages&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-publish-with-netlify-vs-github-pages&quot; aria-label=&quot; 배포방법 publish with netlify vs github pages permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 배포방법 Publish with netlify vs github pages&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee#-gatsby-config&quot;&gt;gatsby-starter-bee&lt;/a&gt; 에서 배포는 netlify와 github pages두가지 배포방법을 제시해놓았다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.outsider.ne.kr/1417&quot;&gt;netlify&lt;/a&gt;는 서버 없이 쉽게 정적페이지를 배포해주는 도구라고한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;깃허브 페이지(GitHub Pages)는 깃허브에서 제공하는 정적 사이트 호스팅 서비스이다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;나는 GitHub Pages를 통해 배포를 해보았다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;denied&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-permission-denied&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-permission-denied&quot; aria-label=&quot; permission denied permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 permission denied&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;gatsby-starter-bee에서는 github pages로 배포하는 방법을 아래 스크립트로 안내해줬다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;js&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;scripts&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;deploy&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;gatsby build &amp;amp;&amp;amp; gh-pages -d public -b master -r &apos;git@github.com:${your github id}/${github page name}.github.io.git&apos;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1058px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 32.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&amp;apos;data:image/png;base64,&amp;apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;error-img&quot; title=&quot;error-img&quot; src=&quot;/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/bb2fd/blog-deploy-error.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/5a46d/blog-deploy-error.png 300w,
/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/0a47e/blog-deploy-error.png 600w,
/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/bb2fd/blog-deploy-error.png 1058w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 1058px) 100vw, 1058px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
하지만... 계속 permission denied 이라고 떴다.
&lt;br&gt;
결국 git action으로 github pages를 배포하게 되었다.
&lt;span id=&quot;gitaction&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;-github-action으로-gh-pages-배포하기&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#-github-action%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-gh-pages-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0&quot; aria-label=&quot; github action으로 gh pages 배포하기 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;🚒 github action으로 gh-pages 배포하기&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;최근에 git action을 통해 배포한 경험이 있어서 git action을 통해 github pages를 배포하기로 했다.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
main 브런치에는 기존 폴더들이, public 폴더에 있는 빌드된 파일들이 gh-pages 브런치에 배포되도록 했다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;✔ main 브런치가 push 될 때 git action이 실행되도록 했다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;yml&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-yml&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-yml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token key atrule&quot;&gt;on&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token key atrule&quot;&gt;push&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;token key atrule&quot;&gt;branches&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; main&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;✔ 기본 root를 gh-pages브런치로 설정 해놔야 한다.
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 704px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 42%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&amp;apos;data:image/png;base64,&amp;apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;gh-pages-img&quot; title=&quot;gh-pages-img&quot; src=&quot;/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/5ebd7/gh-pages.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/5a46d/gh-pages.png 300w,
/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/0a47e/gh-pages.png 600w,
/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/5ebd7/gh-pages.png 704w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;✔ &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/peaceiris/actions-gh-pages&quot;&gt;gitflows 참고 사항은 여기에!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[about]]></title><description><![CDATA[김연화 🥑]]></description><link>https://yeonhwakim.github.io/resume-en/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://yeonhwakim.github.io/resume-en/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 27 Jan 2019 16:21:13 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h1 id=&quot;김연화&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%EA%B9%80%EC%97%B0%ED%99%94&quot; aria-label=&quot;김연화 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;김연화&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;
